  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine the best evaluation for patients with idiopathic
      (unexplained) pancreatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluates the role of endoscopic ultrasonography, given that the minimally invasive
      procedures can diagnosis gallbladder disease as well as pancreatitis abnormalities.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
